# Project map (Film Catalog)

**Первый stop перед ресерчем.** Детали — в sibling rules `00`–`06` и ADR `docs/adr/`.

## Quick lookup

| Ищешь | Открой |
|--------|--------|
| Tier ruby/gold rules | `lib/media/release-tags.ts` → `releaseTier()`; shared predicates → `lib/media/tier-core.ts` |
| Spotlight / ambient color | ADR-0005; `lib/media/tier-presentation.ts`; `components/layout/SpotlightTier.tsx` |
| Catalog filters / facets | `lib/movies/movie-query.ts`, `lib/catalog/catalog-facets.ts`, `lib/catalog/audio-track-scope.ts` |
| Scan / import | `lib/media/scanner.ts`, `lib/media/name-parser.ts`, `lib/media/ffprobe.ts` |
| Build MKV queue | `lib/builds/*`, `scripts/release-build-worker.ts`, ADR-0006 |
| Export / move jobs | `lib/releases/export-*`, `lib/releases/move-*`, `lib/media-jobs/*`, ADR-0007/8/10 |
| Covers | `lib/covers/cover-url.ts`, `lib/covers/cover-storage.ts` |
| Merge / duplicates | `lib/merge/movie-merge.ts`, `lib/merge/duplicate-groups.ts` |
| Franchises | `lib/franchises/franchise-slots.ts`, `franchise-summary.ts` |
| Prisma includes | `lib/movies/movie-include.ts`, `lib/franchises/franchise-include.ts` |
| API validators | `lib/api/validators.ts` + split files in `validators/` |
| UI primitives | `components/primitives/`; domain cards → `components/{movies,builds,…}/` |

## Canonical modules (не дублировать)

| Concern | Module |
|---------|--------|
| File size formatting | `lib/shared/format-bytes.ts` |
| Duration display/ETA | `lib/shared/duration-format.ts` |
| Form duration fields | `lib/shared/duration.ts` |
| Search vs matchKey text | `lib/shared/text-normalize.ts` |
| Codec profile validation | `validateAudioProfileForCodec` in `dictionaries.ts` |
| Tier profile nullify | `nullifyAudioProfile` in `quality-predicates.ts` |
| Export/move UI labels | `lib/media-jobs/job-display.ts` |
| Copy progress string | `lib/media-jobs/job-progress-message.ts` |
| Tier filter combos | `lib/media/tier-core.ts` |

## Anti-patterns

- ❌ Second `formatFileSizeGB` with other rounding — use `formatBytes`
- ❌ Inline ruby/gold if-chains — use `tier-core` / `releaseTier`
- ❌ New export/move status badge maps — extend `buildMediaJobStatusMeta`
- ❌ `normalizeAudioProfile` name for new code — use explicit names above
- ❌ Prisma include ad-hoc — use `movieInclude` / `franchiseInclude`

